narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: This course taught me how to develop an argument and properly convey it through my writing. I learned how to gather information about history and world issues and create my own perspective on those matters.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: This course really forced myself to bring out my creative side and present it on paper. I think that a greater emphasis should be put on writing rather than discussions that take place for the majority of the class.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would recommend this course because it is medium-paced and you know very well what is expected from you.

narratives.question_text: The Canvas course site allowed me to identify and access required course materials easily.
How will you use the knowledge and skills you learned in this course in your future endeavors?
comments: I will use the skills that I have acquired from this course to write clear and concise essays in whatever subject I must write an essay for.
